Osijek.title: Osijek
Osijek.byline: Osijek is a city in Eastern Croatia.

Osiyan.title: Osiyan
Osiyan.byline: Osiyan or "Osian" popularly known as the "Gateway to The Thar Desert", is a small town in Rajasthan, India known for its ancient temple ruins and as a base for camel safaris into the dessert.
